{
  "stem": "2002.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the, the father is bringin' 'em every Sunday to Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The father is, is one of the best husbands in the world you can find, the best father in the world.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I met my son-in-law, he was a laborer for $4 an hour.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I send him to college.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's a lawyer now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he is a lawyer in a firm in Vermont.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he's a partner already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at nighttime, he gives-- he gives-- he teaches in college, like a professor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he gets $75 an hour for, for-- because he's got a brain as a computer-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- yeah, there is a message.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The message is, they are very ethical.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are very-- I can write a book just about my daughter, my son-in-law, and my children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, for an example, in the University of Vermont, this-- in the next week is gonna be a program.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's called Holocaust Survivors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're also going there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The message for them is, is it doesn't-- first of all, I feel the same way if you Jewish or non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My always feeling is to judge the, the person who he is, not what religion he is, and not what-- it-- it to-- to be nice.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To give an example, all my friends are Christians. 99% my friends are Christians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't know how to explain you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and the same thing, I didn't ask my son-in-law, the children to have Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He himself suggested to my wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't ask him to, to, to convert to Judaism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As long they are happy, that's what I was interested in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In [INAUDIBLE], I cannot describe you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's no words.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he's very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he's very bright.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I wouldn't say street bright, but book-- very bright.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
